snippet.title: BOUNDARY Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Teaser trailer for BOUNDARY,The multiplayer tactical space-based shooter that puts players in the role of a heavily armed astronauts in space engaging in fierce zero gravity firefights. Fully customizable loadouts, weapons and ammo types across 6 classes of Astronaut for players to choose from in multiple game modes.

You can follow our twitter @TheScalpels or FB @ProjectBoundary
And our Discord channel https://discord.gg/MDaSJwZ
